sub_title: Director of Connectivity Data Analytics | Technology & Telecoms | Data - AI - Strategy - Innovation | Bridging Technology & Business gap
summary:
Highly skilled professional with a track-record in bridging the business & technology gap. Considerable leadership and consulting experience in the field of innovation, business creativity, strategic thinking, business strategy, digital transformation programs, data programs, data storytelling and analytics translation. 

Natural-born stakeholder manager, advising and collaborating with senior -including VP, MD and C-level-stakeholder field. Extensive international involvement in various organizations, primarily in the technology and telecommunications sectors. 

Holding an international MBA and successfully completed courses in Innovation and Marketing at top tier US business schools. Additional certification in Entrepreneurial Finance and Business & Financial Modeling. Guest lecturer in business creativity and innovation programs at various business schools in Europe and USA. 

Passionate about the art of watchmaking, closely monitoring trends and innovations in this domain.
